      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Yes, TO is a valid Scrabble word worth 2 points in both TWL and SOWPODS. It's one of the most common English prepositions — meaning "in the direction of" or "toward." While only 2 points on its own, TO has perhaps the most 3-letter extensions of any 2-letter word: TOD, TOE, TOG, TOM, TON, TOO, TOP, TOT, TOW, TOY — ten options from a single setup.</p>

